Exploring the World

Monolith Vs Microservices

Monolith means all services in single project

Microservices means different project for different services

Separation of concern

how different services interact with each other?
through calling api hosted on different ports with same domain

2 ways to fetch data from API
1. after page load then API call then render UI
2. after page load then render UI then API call then rerender

use 2nd approach Better UX
useEffect Hook
useEffect(callback, dependency array)
callback will call after component renders

CORS policy

Shimmer UI

conditional rendering used in case on Shimmer UI

whole component gets rerendered

Building Search functionality
1. One list for restaurant search
2. One list for rendering data
